<br />\n<br />\nqs 比較多女仔讀，需求亦都大，當年我fd 英國bba grad入左間sub仔做qs得11000 做左兩年跳出去都19000<br />\n<br />\n總括：既然無工同後生就咩都搵下試下先 人工待遇岩就試下做一排睇下適唔適合"},{"pid":"cc5e193e4be55c5dcbd3b83ed7593af4e46ed30c","tid":454793,"uid":77056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵pc工啦，我都係HD fg 17k 5day</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n男朋友唔俾 話地盤好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同學做pc 起薪都15k 本身都想apply<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁男朋友唔比你食飯你又真係唔撚食？<br />\n大個人啦 係咪番工都要男朋友管撚住先開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982e967ffc5015fa232c84cd2a55b226ad029685","tid":454793,"uid":56900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:13:31.000Z","msg":"女仔直接轉行囉 做engine clerk晒時間"},{"pid":"039194b44af6f910dc303e5567f1ffc0093354e3","tid":454793,"uid":97551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你頂爛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無engine學位？<br />\n我公司最低都12k</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係啊 佢話過左proba 會加我先諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌其實我依個位個個起薪都12k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多人入行都係白紙<br />\n入到再學 <br />\n真係唔好頂爛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d07dfcc0296f7a3534ade17c7d616560ef6749","tid":454793,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:19:51.000Z","msg":"得罪講句, 工程低過1