係做to</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我讀archit 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個陣見畫圖多job ad 嘛<br />\n又等錢使所以做住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁老實講讀Archit 11k係低左d 但樓主你屋企等唔等錢洗先？ <br />\n我覺得如果你只係岩岩遲職無耐就可以等下，搵份好既，始終你有經驗同岩major會好易搵到工（我一開始以為你ive ba) <br />\n<br />\n做pc / ae 雖然人工比較高 但你一黎你唔係engine出身 二黎呢d三殺位黎 壓唔壓得住判頭 又要哄得掂上家 我覺得好睇你個人性格  尤其是你無engine major只能做sub仔 情況只會更慘<br />\n<br />\nqs 比較多女仔讀，需求亦都大，當年我fd 英國bba grad入左間sub仔做qs得11000 做左兩年跳出去都19000<br />\n<br />\n總括：既然無工同後生就咩都搵下試下先 人工待遇岩就試下做一排睇下適唔適合</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我等錢使 屋企應該唔係幾等錢洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽你咁講 PC/AE 應該唔係幾啱我<br />\n本人毒J黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算啦 其實我唔諗住長做 返到黎搵下admin clerk<br />\nover 之前份工12k 就可以塞住我媽把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd9a12f71a644a3fbc91b275a7f462638cb79cf","tid":454793,"uid":125218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得罪講句, 工程低過12K係侮辱緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺 當我intern 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3cb8f2a13686b4a3e356098f17c7a6347e0c2e","tid":454793,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:54:43.000Z","msg":"讀返個pt degree <br />\n早d讀越好<br />\n做咩裸辭 又話份工hea"},{"pid":"28899e0f57ae46c3c6ff56418b566d91a63b2766","tid":454793,"uid":125218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得絲打之前開過post, 唔係好多狗公介紹job 比你架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人溝過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我send 左去個巴打公司到apply bim <br />\n但暫時仲未有回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27c74272fd38bfd65d401108431776643fd0961","tid":454793,"uid":125218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:56:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似係覺得你唔太岩心水 但係又等人用<br />\n所以壓你價 搏你冇工開等錢洗會去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBIM就算新入職一般都有12-13k......<br />\n<br />\n利申 都係今年archi grad 依家畫cad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得係咁 佢話in 完我覺得我對bim 無興趣同無熱誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講真依家都唔係個個都係因為對份工有熱誠先走去apply 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2434cad89973742221ff56cf03b9a5ec2c2578","tid":454793,"uid":125218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:03:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實fg出嚟做draftman個個都係12k起跳，除非你唔做畫圖啦，就可以人工高啲，btw你讀邊科？我建議你就算畫圖都入大公司學，學到一年以上出嚟轉行地盤都有個底，人工又高啲。<br />\n利申：女，由draftman轉咗做pc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我讀archit 啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉 個頭開錯左 我fg 出黎入左間蚊型公司做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實如果想升既話係咪唔應該做畫圖 做啲可以連到地盤既工 畫圖好似無乜career path 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cee63e5fc86a3e03eb6715451443bde0952e99d","tid":454793,"uid":125218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀返個pt degree <br />\n早d讀越好<br />\n做咩裸辭 又話份工hea</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n份工就係太hea 啱啲想做到退休既人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我讀archit 對公司做既嘢完全無概念<br />\n公司仲要得我一個畫圖 又無senior 帶<br />\n孤單作戰好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3631399becad82a65db6611d4dd6ef9a7cb1af75","tid":454793,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排有seconded staff係政府housing做 樓主試下app